## Maintenance

**When updating strategy**:
1. Update version number in all docs
2. Add to version history in FILTERS_SUMMARY.md
3. If filter modified: Update all three docs
4. If new filter: Full documentation in all three
5. Keep examples up-to-date with current defaults

**Consistency checks**:
- Default values match strategy code
- Settings descriptions match tooltips
- Examples use realistic market data
- All filters listed in all three docs

